 "id": "446472061628197", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974796_446472064961530_1805604415805181405_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=B41j5BhVnsIQ7kNvgHHE7Ko&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Arn-yQEeD3GiJh_jbR2H6yU&oh=00_AYC0QSyEsAoDHgWZcmR0gDRpWy0n_cWqnEWipZj_I2HZZg&oe=66F40BE0"}, {"file_name": "AURORA-en_Screenshot-4_2560x1440px.png", "id": "3368616090109593", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031459_3368616093442926_8129509965718289146_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=gjBjyVg4wJkQ7kNvgGMG0Gy&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Arn-yQEeD3GiJh_jbR2H6yU&oh=00_AYBJihbiOwNqvINsLY-VMsxSoxSp0Hjndz-h_hWZxLMTcw&oe=66F3EA22"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "AURORA-en_Video-cover_2560x1440px.png", "id": "312151718532258", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031417_312151721865591_6329849532622027501_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=tfJHqjBugMgQ7kNvgGELBuT&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Arn-yQEeD3GiJh_jbR2H6yU&oh=00_AYAOCnxijFE6Wa5X3nQXz-FFd2xoVqjn7TbWxwQuhARikQ&oe=66F3F860"}, "display_name": "AURORA Lite", "keywords": [], "long_description": "With AURORA you can validate your 3D projects benefiting from the advantages of making it a virtual environment:\n\n\u2705 pre-identify problems in the design.\n\u2705 visualize different finishes of the final product.\n\u2705 minimizes the need for physical prototypes.\n\u2705 save on costs and time during your processes.\n\nIt's very easy and intuitive to use! Once you have imported your 3D model, dive into an environment and start validating your project.\n\nYou have at your disposal a complete toolkit with which you can: \n\u25cf section the 3D model\n\u25cf disassemble by parts,\n\u25cf visualize the finishes\n\u25cf take annotations\n\u25cf take measurements\n\nRequest your free demo and try it for 30 days!", "short_description": "AURORA is a Virtual Reality software that 